<p><strong>3. ЭЛЕКТРИЧЕСКИЙ СИГНАЛ (NRZ)</strong></p>
<div class="svg-container"><svg width="550" height="100" viewBox="0 0 550 100"><line x1="20" y1="50" x2="530" y2="50" stroke="#333" stroke-width="1"/><path d="M30 20 L95 20 L95 80 L160 80 L160 20 L225 20 L225 20 L290 20 L290 80 L355 80 L355 20 L420 20 L420 80 L485 80 L485 50" fill="none" stroke="#0077b6" stroke-width="2.5"/><text x="62" y="15" font-size="10" text-anchor="middle">1</text><text x="127" y="92" font-size="10" text-anchor="middle">0</text><text x="192" y="15" font-size="10" text-anchor="middle">1</text><text x="257" y="15" font-size="10" text-anchor="middle">1</text><text x="322" y="92" font-size="10" text-anchor="middle">0</text><text x="387" y="15" font-size="10" text-anchor="middle">1</text><text x="452" y="92" font-size="10" text-anchor="middle">0</text></svg><p><em>Уровень +5В = бит 1, 0В = бит 0. Прямоугольные импульсы (NRZ — Non-Return to Zero).</em></p></div>

